{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was Jewish doctors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no shortage of medicine because of the transport brought everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- there were hospitals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So if a-- so if a-- if a Swiss Cross-- a-- a-- a Red Cross delegation would come to Auschwitz, they would just show them, look here, we are treating-- we've got excellent hospitals here.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But what-- what the truth was, the hospitals, once it became full, they emptied it out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everybody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the next day, they started admission again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's how it works, the hospital in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was taken to hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had typhoid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what I had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I know, that I have very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't stand on my feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I knew that-- that physically, I-- I-- I knew that some kind of illness I have got.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made all kind of tests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time it came back, the test that I-- that I had typhoid, I was already recovered.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just by your own bodily--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just my own body resistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I recovered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the hospital-- in fact, you had a little bit more food than in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recovered-- not only that I recovered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took from the blood, I think it was 100 centiliter of blood they took for me, for using it for a serum.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a week later, a German SS man came into the hospital and ask for my name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I see a general officer asked specially for my name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he got for me a [NON-ENGLISH], [INAUDIBLE], because you gave the blood, you gave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't give them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
